WEBVTT

00:13:27.345 --> 00:13:30.040
because once we're better able
to allocate value,

00:13:30.064 --> 00:13:33.088
people will use their money
and their energies

00:13:33.112 --> 00:13:35.290
for more constructive things.

00:13:35.727 --> 00:13:38.316
If it cost a fraction of a cent
to send an email,

00:13:38.340 --> 00:13:39.802
would we still have spam?

00:13:40.674 --> 00:13:42.877
We're not at this world yet,

00:13:42.901 --> 00:13:44.358
but it's coming.

00:13:44.382 --> 00:13:48.719
Right now, it's like we're in a world
that is seeing the first automobile.

00:13:49.579 --> 00:13:52.564
The first cryptocurrency,
like the first car,

00:13:53.533 --> 00:13:57.260
is slow and hard to understand
and hard to use.

00:13:58.095 --> 00:14:00.641
Digital money,
like the horse and carriage,